reviewText: DVD arrived in excellent condition, thank you !!

Well, it is another one of those videos where the Lady basically tries to make you aroused by her movements. It can be arousing but to me, after watching a couple of these types of videos, well, it just didn't do anything for me. I would recommend it to anyone who likes watching individual Ladies rubbing oil all over themselves.

Ok, I'm not a big Danni fan. In fact I think her face leaves a lot to be desired, but in fairness it took me most of the video to notice that she--or he others--had faces. And for that I have to give this a five star review!

Danni Ashe is the most downloaded woman on the internet for good reason. Her short frame is all about sex! And this video, while far from being her best, does showcase her amazing breasts in several vignettes. There are other models in this video, but none to compare with Danni. If you're one of her legion of fans, buy this.

About half the 60 minute dvd contains 1992 footage of the remarkable Danni Ashe, in all her beautiful, bare, natural glory.  Unfortunately, the other models have apparently succumbed to the plastic siren call, though one can easily avoid them by skipping to the next enjoyable Danni segment.

Most footage has music overlays with little original sound if it ever existed, though at least one Danni segment definitely has her voice.

This dvd reviewed had digital flaws in the pressing, though most probably it was an exception, and normally one would not have this problem.

Recommended to any Danni Ashe fan for this early footage of her adult modeling career.
